				<p>ExpressionEngine 5.1 has been released and you can now drag and drop files directly onto any File field.</p>

<figure><img src="https://expressionengine.com/asset/img/blog/ee51file.png" style="max-width: 781px"></figure>

<p>This was a natural springboard into answering one of our most common requests: bulk upload to a Grid. You can drag a host of files onto the File Grid field and get a new row for each file. Easy peasy.</p>

<figure><img src="https://expressionengine.com/asset/img/blog/ee51filegrid.gif"></figure>

