<p>This is especially important if you are running <em>any</em> add-ons by <a href="https://eeharbor.com/" title="" rel="external">EEHarbor</a>. Do <strong>not</strong> use the 1-click updater until you&#8217;ve updated all your EEHarbor add-ons with ExpressionEngine 5 compatible versions.&#160;<a href="#fnref:2" class="footnote-backref">&#8617;&#xFE0E;</a></p>
</li>

<li id="fn:3">
<p>If you aren&#8217;t already on ExpressionEngine 4.3.6, the updater will first update you to 4.3.6, then you will need to run it again to get to 5.0.2.&#160;<a href="#fnref:3" class="footnote-backref">&#8617;&#xFE0E;</a></p>
</li>

</ol>
</div>
