<p>ExpressionEngine 3 is entering the tail end of its support life, and is set to retire on December 14, 2018. Once retired, it will no longer receives bug fixes or security patches. You can read more about our end-of-life policy for legacy software on our <a href="https://expressionengine.createsend1.com/t/r-l-jjdljtc-l-y/">version support page</a>.</p>

<p>In celebration of its retirement, all ExpressionEngine upgrades are currently <strong>10% off</strong> until next Friday, September 21st! Upgrade today and enjoy all the <a href="https://expressionengine.com/whats-new">great new features in v4</a>.</p>

