<p>So we don&#8217;t really understand why, but there is apparently a holiday going on from Noon PST through midnight tomorrow in honor of prime numbers. We hate feeling left out, so from now until tomorrow night ONLY, we have repriced ExpressionEngine using only prime numbers:</p>

<ul>
<li>ExpressionEngine 4: <del>$299</del> <strong>$271</strong>

<ul>
<li>Additional Sites: <del>$199</del> <strong>$179/ea</strong></li>
</ul></li>
<li>Upgrade from ExpressionEngine 3: <del>$99</del> <strong>$89</strong>

<ul>
<li>Upgrade from ExpressionEngine 2 to 3: <del>$149</del> <strong>$131</strong></li>
<li>That means you save <strong>$79</strong> total if you then leap to v4!</li>
</ul></li>
</ul>

<p>Don&#8217;t delay, our celebration of prime numbers ends in only 36 hours! Wait&#8230; shouldn&#8217;t that be like 37 hours? Really don&#8217;t understand how this holiday works, oh well!</p>

